<i>noun</i>: 허기 [허기], 시장기 [시장끼], 기아 [기아], 공복감 [공복깜], 공복 [공복] <i>verb</i>: 허기지다 [허기지다], 주리다 [주ː리다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>허기 [허기]</dt><br>
<dd>hunger; starvation</dd><br>
<dd>배가 몹시 고픈 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of feeling extremely hungry.</dd><br>
<dt>시장기 [시장끼]</dt><br>
<dd>hunger</dd><br>
<dd>배가 고픈 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A hungry feeling.</dd><br>
<dt>기아 [기아]</dt><br>
<dd>hunger</dd><br>
<dd>먹을 것이 없어 굶주림.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of starving without food.</dd><br>
<dt>공복감 [공복깜]</dt><br>
<dd>hunger</dd><br>
<dd>음식을 먹지 않아 뱃속이 비어 있는 것과 같은 배고픔.</dd><br>
<dd>Hunger like emptiness in the stomach because one has not eaten food.</dd><br>
<dt>공복 [공복]</dt><br>
<dd>1. empty stomach</dd><br>
<dd>오랫동안 음식을 먹지 않아 비어 있는 뱃속.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which the stomach is empty because the person has not eaten for a long time.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hunger</dd><br>
<dd>배고픔.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being hungry.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>허기지다 [허기지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hunger; be starved</dd><br>
<dd>배가 몹시 고파 기운이 빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>To feel too hungry that all of one's energy is drained.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hunger; desire; want</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상을 간절히 바라거나 탐내다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have a strong desire or craving for a certain object.</dd><br>
<dt>주리다 [주ː리다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. starve</dd><br>
<dd>먹을 것을 제대로 먹지 못하거나 굶다.</dd><br>
<dd>To have no access to proper food or go without eating.</dd><br>
<dd>2. hunger</dd><br>
<dd>원하는 것을 얻지 못하여 몹시 아쉬워하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To be very frustrated since one is unable to get what one wants.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>